
<div class="pure-g">
  <div class="pure-u-3-4">

    <p>Who do you share with and why?</p>

    <p>
      Besides our staff, we share this info with
      {{input type="text" value=model.statement.thirdPartySharingNameOne placeholder="3rd party"}},
      and
      {{input type="text" value=model.statement.thirdPartySharingNameTwo placeholder="3rd party"}}
      in order to
      {{input type="text" value=model.statement.thirdPartySharingPurpose placeholder="take action connected to the purpose for collection"}}.
    </p>

    {{#each model.statement.sharingParties as |party|}}
      <div>
        <p>
          We also share this info with
          {{input type="text" value=party.nameOne placeholder="3rd party"}},
          and
          {{input type="text" value=party.nameTwo placeholder="3rd party"}}
          in order to
          {{input type="text" value=party.purpose placeholder="take action connected to the purpose for collection"}}.
        </p>
      </div>
    {{/each}}

    <p>
      <button {{action "addParty"}} class="pure-button">we have another reason</button>
    </p>

    {{#link-to "steps.step" 5 classNames="pure-button button-blue next-step-button"}}move along{{/link-to}}
  </div>

  <div class="pure-u-1-4">
    <button {{action "toggleHelp"}} type="button" class="pure-button button-black-on-white help-text-button">Is that a problem?</button>

    {{#if showHelp}}
        <div id="help-text" class="help-text">
            <p>
              You need to have a valid reason to share information with outside parties, related to your purpose for collecting it. This doesn’t apply if you gathered the information from a public source, or you have asked the user’s permissions.
            </p>

            <p>
              See <a href="https://privacy.org.nz/limits-on-use-of-personal-information-principle-ten/">Privacy Principle 10</a>,
              and <a href="https://privacy.org.nz/limits-on-disclosure-of-personal-information-principle-eleven/#collection">Privacy Principle 11</a>
              for more.
            </p>

        </div>
    {{/if}}
  </div>
</div>
